Titolo: The King of Chicago

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: The King of Chicago is a 1986 action-adventure video game by Doug Sharp. Based on numerous Hollywood mobster movies, this game is set in the 1930s, but some sequences towards the end of the game take place in 1986. The Macintosh version of the game is animated using claymation, while other versions utilize drawn graphics.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
